ds%20or%20a%20partner%20sharing%20the%20space.%20Likewise%2C%20working%20or%20relaxing%20in%20the%20same%20area%20where%20you%20cook%20can%20be%20distracting%20if%20you%20have%20made%20something%20with%20a%20strong%20odor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223556%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Open-concept%20living%20room%20with%20tall%20ceilings%20and%20wood%20floors%20and%20white%20and%20gray%20furniture%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6849f36985e81483682bed17%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOpen-concept%20homes%20are%20going%20out%20of%20style.%3Cp%3EBreadmaker%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40julianaghani%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EJuliana%20Ghani%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20interior%20designer%20from%20Minneapolis%2C%20agreed%2C%20saying%20that%20seeing%20your%20kitchen%20constantly%20can%20also%20make%20a%20home%20feel%20less%20welcoming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20open-concept%20kitchen%20is%20drawn%20out%20at%20this%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20Ghani%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20one%20in%20my%20condo%20right%20now%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%20a%20fan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20hosting%2C%20your%20guests%20see%20everything%20that's%20going%20on%2C%20which%20some%20may%20like%2C%20but%20they%20can%20see%20your%20dirty%20dishes.%20They%20can%20see%20the%20pots%20and%20pans%20that%20you%20use%20to%20cook%2C%26quot%3B%20Ghani%20said%2C%20which%20isn't%20relaxing%20and%20doesn't%20create%20a%20party%20vibe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20same%20can%20be%20true%20of%20seeing%20your%20dishes%20or%20just%20the%20look%20of%20a%20kitchen%20when%20you're%20having%20downtime%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGhani%20told%20BI%20that%20many%20of%20her%20clients%20are%20turning%20toward%20a%20%26quot%3Bcozy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnancy-meyers-home-aesthetic-interior-design-tips-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENancy%20Meyers%20aesthetic%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20an%20open%20concept.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Eustace%20said%20you%20can%20make%20your%20open%20floor%20plan%20work%20for%20you%20by%20not%20decorating%20it%20solely%20based%20on%20trends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20about%20tailoring%20things%20that%20you%20see%20that%20you're%20inspired%20by%20and%20using%20them%20to%20fit%20your%20personal%20needs%20and%20lifestyle%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Eustace%20doesn't%20have%20open%20shelving%20in%20her%20kitchen%20because%20she%20has%20trouble%20keeping%20them%20organized%2C%20while%20Ghani%20said%20she%20loves%20her%20open%20shelves%20and%20that%20they%20help%20her%20keep%20her%20glassware%20minimalist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22025cb967-bbc5-4ee2-8213-7c50ed922939%5C%22%3EDon't%20forget%20about%20zoning%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEustace%20told%20BI%20that%20improper%20zoning%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20issue%26quot%3B%20in%20open-concept%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20what%20people%20tend%20to%20do%20because%20it's%20open%20concept%20is%20think%20of%20the%20whole%20space%20as%20one%20huge%20room%20when%20the%20best%20design%20thinks%20about%20each%20space%20as%20an%20individual%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20Eustace%20said%2C%20aka%20zoning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20some%20people%20think%20zoning%20means%20putting%20up%20a%20bookcase%20or%20other%20divider%20between%20areas%2C%20but%20Eustace%20said%20it's%20better%20to%20just%20decorate%20each%20space%20individually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20should%20think%20about%20a%20lighting%20plan%20for%20each%20specific%20area%20rather%20than%20just%20a%20lighting%20plan%20for%20the%20whole%20kitchen%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20open-concept%20home%20with%20