c%2C%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2025%2F05%2F28%2Fai-jobs-white-collar-unemployment-anthropic%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAxios%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Amodei%20warned%20that%20AI%20companies%20and%20governments%20needed%20to%20stop%20%26quot%3Bsugarcoating%26quot%3B%20the%20potential%20for%20mass%20job%20losses%20in%20white-collar%20industries%20like%20finance%2C%20law%2C%20and%20consulting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%2C%20as%20the%20producers%20of%20this%20technology%2C%20have%20a%20duty%20and%20an%20obligation%20to%20be%20honest%20about%20what%20is%20coming%2C%26quot%3B%20Amodei%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20estimated%20that%20AI%20could%20spike%20unemployment%20by%20up%20to%2020%25%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20and%20may%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ceo-warning-ai-could-eliminate-jobs-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeliminate%20half%20of%20entry-level%20white-collar%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20within%20that%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoffman%20said%20he%20had%20called%20the%20Anthropic%20CEO%20to%20discuss%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B'Bloodbath'%20is%20a%20very%20good%20way%20to%20grab%20internet%20headlines%2C%20media%20headlines%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoffman%20said.%20(Axios%2C%20not%20Amodei%2C%20used%20the%20phrase%20%26quot%3Bwhite-collar%20bloodbath.%26quot%3B)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20Hoffman%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bbloodbath%20just%20implies%20everything%20going%20away.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20disagreed%20with%20this%20assessment%2C%20believing%20that%20transformation%2C%20not%20mass%20elimination%2C%20of%20jobs%20is%20a%20more%20likely%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDario%20is%20right%20that%20over%20a%20decade%20or%20three%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20massive%20set%20of%20job%20transformation%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoffman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20compared%20it%20to%20the%20introduction%20of%20tools%20like%20Microsoft%20Excel%2C%20which%20were%20believed%20by%20some%20at%20the%20time%20to%20mark%20the%20end%20of%20accountancy%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20the%20accountant%20job%20got%20broader%2C%20richer%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoffman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BJust%20because%20a%20function's%20coming%20that%20has%20a%20replacement%20area%20on%20a%20certain%20set%20of%20tasks%20doesn't%20mean%20all%20of%20this%20job's%20going%20to%20get%20replaced.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20AI%20eliminating%20roles%2C%20Hoffman%20predicted%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20at%20least%20have%20many%20years%2C%20if%20not%20a%20long%20time%2C%20of%20person-plus-AI%20doing%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoffman%20isn't%20the%20only%20business%20leader%20to%20question%20Amodei's%20AI%20doomsday%20prophecy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20VivaTech%20in%20Paris%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-nvidia-anthropic-dario-amodei-ai-jobs-vivatech-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20he%20and%20Amodei%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20much%20disagree%20with%20almost%20everything%26quot%3B%20on%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%2C%20he%20believes%20that%20AI%20is%20so%20scary%20that%20only%20they%20should%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said.%20%26quot%3BTwo%2C%20that%20AI%20is%20so%20expensive%2C%20nobody%20else%20should%20do%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BAnd%20three%2C%20AI%20is%20so%20incredibly%20powerful%20that%20everyone%20will%20lose%20their%20jobs%2C%20which%20explains%20why%20they%20should%20be%20the%20only%20company%20building%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freid-hoffman-linke