%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-18T154519.885_11zon-1750241746-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-18T154519.885_11zon-1750241746-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-451367%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAvinash%20and%20Namita%20used%20fresh%20flowers%20as%20part%20of%20the%20decoration%20for%20all%20the%20wedding%20events%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20parents%20also%20helped%20the%20couple%20in%20planning%20the%20low-waste%20wedding.%20The%20bride%E2%80%99s%20mother%2C%20Priya%20Manohar%20(55)%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20the%20thought%20of%20planning%20such%20an%20unconventional%20wedding%20felt%20overwhelming%2C%20but%20my%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20courage%20and%20belief%20that%20it%20was%20possible%20put%20all%20our%20fears%20to%20rest.%20We%20broke%20down%20the%20entire%20process%2C%20looking%20at%20each%20element%20individually%2C%20considering%20what%20was%20really%20needed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20upcycling%20unused%20saris%20into%20statement%20outfits%20to%20avoiding%20plastic%20in%20the%20decor%20or%20for%20consumables%20like%20water%2C%20every%20detail%20was%20carefully%20planned.%20We%20used%20cruelty-free%20products%20for%20bridal%20makeup.%20We%20also%20used%20palm%20leaf%20straws%20for%20the%20coconut%20water%20that%20we%20served%20our%20guests%2C%20and%20steel%20glasses%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F365696%2Fonam-sadhya-recipes-avial-kalan-olan-erissery-palada-pradhaman-kerala-chef-pillai-shamees-kitchen%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eserve%20payasam%20and%20buttermilk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20during%20the%20sadhya.%20True%20to%20our%20South%20Indian%20roots%2C%20we%20embraced%20banana%20leaves%20for%20serving%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20times%20when%20vendors%20were%20unsure%20about%20what%20we%20wanted.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20wedding%20festivities%2C%20no%20plastic%20bottles%20were%20used.%20Instead%2C%20the%20couple%20set%20up%20water%20coolers%20at%20the%20venue%2C%20and%20the%20guests%20use%20glasses%20rather%20than%20disposable%20cups.%20At%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20wedding%20hall%2C%20guests%20were%20welcomed%20with%20cooling%20dispensers%20offering%20refreshing%20watermelon%20juice%20and%20lemonade%2C%20served%20in%20reusable%20glasses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-18T153418.676_11zon-1750241078.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20used%20palm%20leaf%20straws%20for%20the%20coconut%20water%20that%20they%20served%20to%20the%20guests%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-18T153418.676_11zon-1750241078.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-18T153418.676_11zon-1750241078-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-18T153418.676_11zon-1750241078-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-18T153418.676_11zon-1750241078-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-18T153418.676_11zon-1750241078-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-451354%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20couple%20used%20palm%20leaf%20straws%20for%20the%20coconut%20water%20that%20they%20served%20to%20the%20guests%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20keeping%20with%20their%20commitment%20to%20reducing%20waste%2C%20even%20the%20wedding%20favours%20were%20thoughtfully%20curated.%20Instead%20of%20traditional%2C%20single-use%20items%2C%20the%20duo%20decided%20to%20offer%20eco-friendly%20gifts.%20Their%20zero-waste%20hampers%20included%20locally%20sourced%20spices%20and%20snacks%20packed%20in%20paper%20bags%2C%20which%20were%20then%20gifted%20in%20fabric%20pouches%20made%20by%20differently-abled%20artisans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20not%20just%20a%20personal%20celebration%20for%20us%3B%20it%20created%20meaningful%20moments%20for%20everyone%20involved%2C%20gently%20touching%20lives%20and%20spreading%20smiles%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%20bride%E2%80%99s%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%E2%80%99s%20determination%20not%20to%20compromise%20on%20their%20low-waste%20vision%20did%20bring%20in%20a%20few%20challenges.%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20biggest%20hurdles%20was%20getting%20the%20hotel%20to%20stop%20serving%20plastic%20bottles%20in%20the%20rooms%2C%E2%80%9D%20Avinash%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20though%20we%20had%20requested%20glass%20bottles%2C%20they%20initially%20insisted%20on%20providing%20plastic%20ones.%20Then%2C%20we%20suggested%20sourcing%20the%20bottles%20ourselves%20for%20the%20guests.%20It%20took%20some%20back%20and%20forth%2C%20but%20in%20the%20end%2C%20the%20hotel%20agreed%2C%20and%20that%20was%20a%20big%20win.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENamita%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20times%20when%20vendors%20were%20unsure%20about%20what%20we%20wanted.%20I%20think%20they%20thought%20we%20were%20being%20too%20specific%20or%20too%20demanding.%20But%20in%20the%20end%2C%20we%20all%20worked%20together%2C%20and%20the%20results%20were%20better%20than%20we%20could%20have%20imagined.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20they%20pulled%20off%20a%20low-waste%20celebration%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F412131%2Fupcycling-old-clothes-for-a-sustainable-future%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ededication%20to%20reducing%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E%20paid%20off%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20event.%20The%20total%20wet%20waste%20generated%20from%20the%201200-person%20wedding%20was%20only%20100%20kilograms%2C%20which%20is%20an%20astonishingly%20low%20amount%2C%20especially%20considering%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20event.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20so%20proud%20of%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20groom.%20%E2%80%9CNormally%2C%20you%20will%20expect%20far%20more%20waste%20from%20an%20event%20of%20this%20size%2C%20but%20with%20proper%20planning%20and%20the%20support%20of%20everyone%20involved%2C%20we%20kept%20it%20to%20a%20minimum.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-18T153731.037_11zon-1750241266.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Giant%20palm%20leaves%20were%20used%20to%20create%20a%20flower-shaped%20art%20in%20the%20background%20of%20the%20wedding%20stage%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-06-18T153731.037_11zon-1750241266.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-W