create%20a%20nationwide%2C%20decentralised%20system%20for%20recycling%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jayesh.%20%E2%80%9COne%20that%E2%80%99s%20accessible%2C%20ethical%2C%20and%20completely%20transparent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStories%20from%20the%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScrapdeal%E2%80%99s%20impact%20goes%20beyond%20just%20numbers.%20Its%20user%20reviews%20tell%20a%20story%20of%20growing%20environmental%20consciousness%20among%20everyday%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHave%20been%20their%20customer%20for%20many%20years%20now.%20They%20collect%20scrap%20from%20our%20society%20regularly.%20I%20had%20placed%20a%20request%20to%20collect%20my%204-wheeler%20tyres%2C%20and%20they%20came%20the%20very%20next%20day%20and%20gave%20the%20promised%20weighted%20price%2C%E2%80%9D%20Naveen%20Gupta%2C%20a%20Scrapdeal%20customer%2C%20shares%20with%20TBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20true%20sense%2C%20a%20service%20to%20society.%20People%20should%20support%20them.%20This%20will%20help%20them%20to%20achieve%20the%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Mission%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rajesh%20Shekhawat.%20The%20team%20also%20conducts%20awareness%20sessions%20in%20schools%20and%20societies%2C%20encouraging%20citizens%20to%20embrace%20sustainable%20habits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-59_11zon-1750262268.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20nearly%2090%25%20repeat%20users%20and%20growing%20trust%2C%20Scrapdeal%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20a%20service%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20system%20people%20return%20to.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-59_11zon-1750262268.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-59_11zon-1750262268-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-59_11zon-1750262268-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-59_11zon-1750262268-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-59_11zon-1750262268-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-451674%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20nearly%2090%25%20repeat%20users%20and%20growing%20trust%2C%20Scrapdeal%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20a%20service%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20system%20people%20return%20to.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20search%20for%20a%20kabadiwala%20or%20recycling%20centre%20anymore.%20Just%20open%20the%20app%20and%20help%20the%20planet%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jayesh%20says.%20Today%2C%20we%20are%20having%20collaborations%20with%20more%20than%20500%20residential%20societies%20and%20100%2B%20corporations%2C%20where%20we%20regularly%20arrange%20recyclable%20waste%20collection%20drives%20and%20do%20doorstep%20collection%20as%20well.%20Some%20of%20them%20are%20Sun%20Universe%20Society%2C%20Yuthika%20Apartment%2C%20Ved%20Vihar%20Apartment%2C%20Sonigara%20Kesar%20Society%2C%20and%20many%20more.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMore%20than%201%20lakh%20people%20have%20already%20connected%20with%20us%20through%20our%20activities%20and%20applications%20with%20almost%2080-90%25%20of%20our%20customer%20retention%20rate%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claims%20proudly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20it%20matters%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20generates%20over%2062%20million%20tonnes%20of%20waste%20annually%2C%20and%20a%20large%20portion%20of%20it%20is%20never%20recycled.%20Platforms%20like%20Scrapdeal%20offer%20a%20glimpse%20into%20how%20this%20can%20change%20%E2%80%94%20not%20through