%20most%20wasteful%20parts%20of%20protein%20packaging%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Soorya.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20different.%20From%20the%20beginning%2C%20we%20chose%20glass%20jars%20for%20our%20packaging%2C%20even%20though%20plastic%20was%20cheaper%20and%20more%20common.%20Despite%20the%20higher%20cost%2C%20we%20were%20committed%20to%20sustainability%20and%20refused%20to%20compromise%20on%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInstead%20of%20contributing%20to%20the%20growing%20plastic%20problem%2C%20we%20created%20biodegradable%20scoops%20that%20would%20break%20down%20naturally%20into%20the%20soil%2C%20reducing%20waste%20and%20supporting%20sustainability%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECosmix%20is%20also%20one%20of%20the%20first%20companies%20in%20the%20wellness%20industry%20to%20embrace%20this%20innovative%20packaging%20solution.%20The%20biodegradable%20scoops%20became%20a%20talking%20point%20for%20the%20brand%2C%20and%20they%20differentiated%20themselves%20from%20other%20protein%20supplement%20brands%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20always%20listen%20to%20our%20customers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vibha.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20them%20asked%20us%20not%20to%20send%20scoops%20with%20our%20products%2C%20while%20others%20preferred%20having%20them.%20We%20had%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20that%20worked%20for%20everyone.%E2%80%9D%20After%20much%20consideration%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20develop%20scoops%20made%20from%20biodegradable%20material%2C%20which%20uses%20husks%20and%20starch.%20These%20scoops%20are%20specifically%20designed%20for%20food%20products%20and%20are%20made%20from%20plant-based%20materials%20that%20naturally%20break%20down%20into%20nutrient-rich%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-B