s%20everything%20%E2%80%94%20passion%2C%20planning%2C%20and%20purpose.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20makes%20him%20exceptional%2C%E2%80%9D%20Malay%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20terrain%20shifted%2C%20so%20did%20the%20challenges.%20Flat%20roads%20gave%20way%20to%20steep%20gradients%2C%20rocky%20trails%2C%20and%20muddy%2C%20landslide-prone%20paths.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20India-Nepal%20border%2C%20things%20got%20harder.%20Nepal%E2%80%99s%20roads%20can%20be%20rough%20in%20places%2C%20and%20there%20were%20sections%20where%20I%20had%20to%20carry%20the%20cycle%20on%20my%20back.%20Especially%20near%20the%20higher%20altitudes%2C%20where%20the%20oxygen%20levels%20drop%2C%20it%20becomes%20more%20of%20a%20battle%20against%20your%20own%20body.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20climb%20beyond%20comfort%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20Salleri%2C%20the%20real%20climb%20began.%20Each%20day%20meant%20pushing%20the%20body%20a%20little%20further%20past%20what%20seemed%20possible.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20no%20longer%20about%20riding.%20The%20roads%20were%20too%20bad%20or%20nonexistent%20in%20places.%20I%20had%20to%20walk%20with%20my%20cycle%2C%20carry%20it%20over%20boulders%20and%20narrow%20tracks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20stretches%20where%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20ride%20at%20all.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FTBI-featured-image-79_11zon-1750081388.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rocky%20terrains%2C%20jungles%2C%20tedious%20treks%3A%20The%20journey%20to%20Everest%20base%20camp%20was%20not%20an%20easy%20one.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FTBI-featured-image-79_11zon-1750081388.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterind